Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透在等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有落下东西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:02:01.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,300)\be1}下雨天就来泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  昨天晚饭后我发过信息给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到那条信息哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的袜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了穿另一边的袜子了  呜呜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话还不如光脚走呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小…小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你内裤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连这都没注意到也实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是太没脑子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要蹲下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会从前面看到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太困了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那样的理由吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这种事情都会有吗  真的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:11.56,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  谁都会有落下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然内裤不是普通的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你一定认为我没有内裤了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦  不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这样了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透也真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  就只有早上比较糊涂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太困了  迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经穿上了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是以为说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  伦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:03:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下午的课堂笔记能借我抄一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这么说来你昨天早退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哟  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么语言？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  是日语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课的时候我被睡魔侵袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不只是早上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点潦草吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有那回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看不清的地方的话  就要问我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  优子  等下也借我看看哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哟  抄完了的话就给伦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚是近视眼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视力有多少呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2.0  这只是装饰眼镜罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  为什么要戴装饰眼镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不戴的话…就会看到一些不该看到的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你说的…莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  现在在优子的背后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  只是胡说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了只是玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个值得一耍的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是近视眼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的别再吓我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我对这种恐怖的事情最没辙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚的演技真好  都能进话剧部了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是话剧部的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是幽灵部员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:11.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}出自夏目漱石的短篇小说「心」  下文翻译为中文原版翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这个夏天  我收到你二三封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得确实是第二封信  你托我在东京找个适当的工作…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.10,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  想去厕所什么的太丢脸了我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  我的头好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  你捂的是肚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊也不是  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去厕所  我带优子去保健室然后顺带去一次可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉啊  伦  真是帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  因为我也想去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  伦也想去厕所？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道怎么回事  但是很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是犯了什么病…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去厕所吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还是保健室？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  厕所  厕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕…厕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}首字母发音都是TO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  应该是透啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  你搞错了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦她突然失去意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天保健室老师也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来  去联络别的老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人  都安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是睡眠不足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带伞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上明明是晴天的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这也只是小雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑回家的话没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:55.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雨女即百鬼夜行中能呼风唤雨的神，现在也指外出即下雨的女性。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我发现了…我其实是雨女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把身体伸出去啦  快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊  猥琐地盯着这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小伦现在都这副样子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这所学校  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦  必须快点擦干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  穿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不需要打伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这个年纪了穿这个有点紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是小学生的话那就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  确实是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿情侣装确实有点不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}翻译：小伦把きつい的意思理解错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就只一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:17.24,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就不穿了  反正我也完全淋湿了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.24,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我远点！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  还以为你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  你湿透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家很近  去我那里烘干吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还在下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在学校里面住着雨女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是暴雨  只要快点跑就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都湿了就不可怕了呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  如果只是去渚家的距离…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想被淋湿  叫个出租车好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本的出租车费用是世界上最贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做着不像高中生该做的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等会儿的话  会不会停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说叫个出租车…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走喽  小渚的家在这边吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！  等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  别丢下我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨什么的明明会使人忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们却那么开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是青春啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:47.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,80)\fad(500,0)}鬼\N头\N老\N师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,70)\fad(300,0)}爱\N好\N：\N写\N诗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了  下雨了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(40,90)}诗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:52.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,80)}现\N实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:11:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊快去洗澡吧去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？大哥已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚  原来你有哥哥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥  现在朋友来我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要占用盥洗室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚是称呼哥哥为大哥的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是称呼他为哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大哥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  浴缸一次只能容纳两人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成2个组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  石头剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我和伦先去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想起来才发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今还没和透单独聊过天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说点什么好呢  这种时候的沉默有点  有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉她们要洗很久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很多DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真正存在的恐怖都市传说」和继续沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要哪个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是究极的选择…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  把衣服脱了放在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点钻进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  你是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我是伦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一根刘海…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以改变一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这反应…腻了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个人都清爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不洗快点她们就没法洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  不快点跟小透和优子交换的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我的房间里只有她们两个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  因为他们很要好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  说起来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  不行了  再这样下去真不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦  把眼睛闭上就不可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才想喊呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了快去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  优子  浴室空出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  不好啦  优子石化啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:45.39,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可怕啊  终于可以洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  透？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  透你有没有过洗头时因为看不到前面而觉得很可怕的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小时候很不擅长用洗发露洗头的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗发露进眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么鬼啊透
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷头在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛杯具啦…眼睛杯具啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  优子  你们两个很吵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  不要啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我还以为自己要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识开始朦胧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  看  我看到绿洲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚  伦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  浴缸的水温  如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  把暖气关掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把衣服烘干而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多都干了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨会不会马上停啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时还不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下的真久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天就如头发一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的好像就是噼里啪啦一下子倒下来那种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是散开的  完全不会缠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为发质不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我摸摸优子的头发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子的头发好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  搞起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这衣服好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动哦  因为现在是关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  输掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想来一局？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要刷新渚的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子的手指挺漂亮的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时应该有修剪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有特别去弄过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很舒服  但是有点不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？透…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我要怎么做才好嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:06.20,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}还是没有要停的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.97,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}下的可真久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:12.18,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但是我还是很喜欢雨的声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.25,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这种心情我也懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:17.31,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:21.20,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好啦  渚  你也把眼睛闭上倾听雨声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:25.50,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哎…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实不坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总感觉听到什么烧起来的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？是我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  回家路上小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  你还借我们伞真是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这伞真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确啊  啊  雨还是好大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下班电车是几点的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥  可以用盥洗室了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经说过  要你们路上小心点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了  下集柚多谷和美宝莲要登场了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我苦守贞洁15年了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  人生回顾到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.61,0:24:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我们好像在第一话里说过会出场的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.06,0:24:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么说了也只会在OP里出现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  A频道  同级生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.83,0:24:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不光是同级生  高年级组当然也是会登场的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------INJP-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:05.07,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放課後予定もなんもないし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:09.92,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨が降ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:12.52,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うちに集合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:20.37,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君は普段から素直じゃないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:24.25,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日はきっと分かるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:30.37,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔がみたいだけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:40.27,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな所にかくれないでいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:44.17,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとほら近づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:47.87,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみも友達だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:55.95,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これから何度も過ぎていく季節も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:59.64,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとほら近くにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:05.67,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみと一緒にいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:13.52,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみと笑ってたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------INCN-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:05.07,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下课后没有任何活动的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:09.92,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为雨一直下着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:12.52,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:20.37,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平时就不怎么率直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:24.25,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也一定可以明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:30.37,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你的笑脸很像我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:40.27,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必躲藏在那个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:44.17,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我们靠得更近些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:47.87,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:55.95,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来将要度过的各种季节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:59.64,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会一直都在你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:05.67,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你在一起哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:13.52,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起欢笑
